data.description: If you're looking for the perfect ranch in a peaceful area, look no further!  This true 3 bedroom home is nestled perfectly in the heart of Westin Hills and backs to the beautiful pond and walking trail.  Brand new kitchen appliances, freshly painted both inside and out, roof new in 2018, furnace in 2022, new carpet in October 2022, and true hardwood floors added to the kitchen/dining room in 2018.  The list of updates goes on and on.  Check this home out today!  The views are spectacular!
